</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_222" id="110r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_222_r1l1"><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Johannſ<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd <expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Otten Pfallncʒgrafen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_222_r1l3">bey Reyn vnd <expan>hercʒog<ex>en</ex></expan> in Peyern etc </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_222_r1l4">Gnedıgen <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> als vns eẅr <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> vnd ein <expan>abſchr<ex>ift</ex></expan> wıe dıe </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_222_r1l5">von Tachaw vnd etlıch <expan>and<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>geſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . damıt ge = </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_222_r1l6">ſandt habt etc das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> Vnd tun <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> für = </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_222_r1l7"><expan>ſtenlıche<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> ʒu <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> daʒ auf dıſʒ ʒeıt niht rat bey vns was </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_222_r1l8">alſo <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır <expan>dıeſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> brıef an <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> freẅnde des </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_222_r1l9">Rats <expan>brıng<ex>en</ex></expan> / vnd <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> bey <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> ſelbs <expan>botſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> in kürcʒ ein </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_222_r1l10">antwurt <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> tun / Denn wo wır <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>fürſtenl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> dıenſt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_222_line_1577133727691_1581">vnd <expan>wolgefall<ex>e</ex>n</expan> etc / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>ſab<ex>at</ex>o</expan> poſt Erhardj </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_222" id="110r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Johanns<ex>en</ex></expan> und <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Otten,
                        pfallnczgrafen bey Reyn und <expan>herczog<ex>en</ex></expan> in Peyern
                        etc.</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Gnedigen <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, als uns ewr
                                <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan>
<expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> und ein
                            <expan>abschr<ex>ift</ex></expan>, wie die von Tachaw und etlich
                                <expan>and<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>geschr<ex>iben</ex></expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, damit gesandt habt etc., das
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol
                            <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> und tun <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fürstenliche<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> zu <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz auf
                        disz zeit niht rat bey uns was; also <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir
                                <expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> brief an <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        frewnde des rats <expan>bring<ex>en</ex></expan> und
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> bey <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> selbs
                                <expan>botsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> in kürcz ein antwurt
                                <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> tun. Denn wo wir
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fürstenl<ex>ichen</ex></expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> dienst und
                            <expan>wolgefall<ex>e</ex>n</expan> etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>sab<ex>at</ex>o</expan> post Erhardi.</ab>
</div>
